---
title: Chicken Tikka with Garlic Rice for Dinner with a Chicken Tikka & Mint Wrap for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new spin on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day! Serve up a mildly spiced chicken tikka on fragrant garlic rice, then pack up an Indian chicken and salad wrap to enjoy the next day for lunch. Extra delicious!

